    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "UNITED\nAIR LINES\nSanta Catalina Island's colorful Casino is\ntypical of the scenic variety of Southern Cali-\nfornia. On United this inviting vacationland\nis just a few hours from your city.\nPROGRESS\n50\nTH ANNIVERSARY FIGHT\nOF POWERED\nSECURITY\nUNITED AIR LINES • ROUTE OF THE MAINLINERS\nSPEED\nYOUR MAIL\n095,22",
